                "text": "MEHT is committed to the provision of a service that is fair, accessible and meets the need of all individuals"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 48,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "prefix": 9.0,
                "text": "Audit and monitoring"
            }
        },
        {
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 49,
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 9.1,
                "text": "Pharmacy will monitor all prescriptions for methadone or other opioid replacement therapy, and any concerns will be reported to the physician responsible for the patient and/or referred to the Drug and Alcohol Liaison Team. Similarly, any concerns from the Drug and Alcohol Liaison Team will be reported to the physician responsible for the patient."
            }
        },
